overview:
Net Semi stocks Obsolete, Military, End of Life, and hard to find components. With over 150000 items in stock Net Semi is sure to have the part you are looking for. Net Semi also sources products for OEMS, CM, and ODMs. Net Semi is a leading provider of electronic components. If you cannot find what you are looking for chances are WE CAN!!

Net Semi is located in the United States and has been selling to fortune 100 to 500 companies for the past 5 years.

Electrical engineers have relied on Net Semi to provide them with obsolete and hard to find components.

You can check inventory levels on any part number at

http://netsemi.com/RequestForQuote.aspx
